    "name": "Mechjestic",
    "steam_appid": 2291210,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对弗罗莲青蛙和她的机甲“铁蝌蚪”来说，生活可不容易。通过收集卡牌并在卡牌对战中打造可自定义机甲，对抗邪恶昆虫和入侵者，这是一款蒸汽朋克风格的Roguelike卡组构筑游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291210/extras/606de0ef9f5637f17377e3b86184c89c.poster.avif?t=1748886633\" width=594 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291210/extras/606de0ef9f5637f17377e3b86184c89c.webm?t=1748886633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291210/extras/606de0ef9f5637f17377e3b86184c89c.mp4?t=1748886633\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >上机甲吧，小蝌蚪</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过收集和构建装备卡组，你可以打出这些卡牌来改变机甲并获得战斗属性。使用同一套装的五个部位还能获得特殊加成！机甲的核心——引擎，也可以更换。不同引擎有不同的加成，比如增加燃料或让你抽更多卡牌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291210/extras/7c6e4de0c529dc7c0089451454253757.poster.avif?t=1748886633\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291210/extras/7c6e4de0c529dc7c0089451454253757.webm?t=1748886633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291210/extras/7c6e4de0c529dc7c0089451454253757.mp4?t=1748886633\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >幸运属于勇敢者……也属于有策略的人</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗中抽到完全没用的卡牌？别担心，燃料系统让你有机会逆转局势。打出卡牌或升级引擎都需要消耗燃料。如果你对手牌不满意，这个灵活的系统允许你将卡牌回收为燃料和机会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291210/extras/54ed4c1da0f731c84b8e1977e19f4515.poster.avif?t=1748886633\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291210/extras/54ed4c1da0f731c84b8e1977e19f4515.webm?t=1748886633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291210/extras/54ed4c1da0f731c84b8e1977e19f4515.mp4?t=1748886633\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无尽之池</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一层都被迷雾笼罩，玩家需要在谜题、宝藏和敌人间穿梭。所有行动都需要行动点和重启点。缺乏其中任意一种都会让你更接近失败并需要重新开始。每通过10层，就会有更强大的Boss出现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291210/extras/fc5f1ef97a40aa9f3fa83d5f444e7714.poster.avif?t=1748886633\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291210/extras/fc5f1ef97a40aa9f3fa83d5f444e7714.webm?t=1748886633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291210/extras/fc5f1ef97a40aa9f3fa83d5f444e7714.mp4?t=1748886633\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mechjestic正在开发中，感谢以下支持与资助：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291210/extras/7d219b3295e5381d30d375ba81b59c15.avif?t=1748886633\" width=600 height=258 /></span></p>",
